# Kardon, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Kardon () is a rural locality (a selo) in Tarbagataysky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 164 as of 2010. There are 6 streets.
Geography
Kardon is located 15&nbsp;km north of Tarbagatay (the district's administrative centre) by road. Shaluty is the nearest rural locality.
